<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">关于</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">从学术研究到商业实践的技术探索之路</p>
    
    <!-- 时间线布局 -->
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
          <div class="marker-icon">🎓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-badge">教育背景</div>
          <h3>学术研究与技术沉淀</h3>
          <p>国科大硕士在读，具备扎实的编程基础与实践经验，专注于人工智能与Web开发领域。深入研究遥感图像处理、机器学习与深度学习技术。</p>
          <div class="timeline-tags">
            <span>硕士在读</span>
            <span>AI研究</span>
            <span>编程基础</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
          <div class="marker-icon">💼</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-badge">商业实践</div>
          <h3>项目经验与市场验证</h3>
          <p>运营闲鱼账号承接项目，累计成交额超万元。涵盖Python编程、遥感处理、网页设计、WebGIS开发、算法设计等多个技术领域，具备良好的客户沟通与项目交付能力。</p>
          <div class="timeline-tags">
            <span>万元+收入</span>
            <span>多领域项目</span>
            <span>客户好评</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
          <div class="marker-icon">🚀</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-badge">技术探索</div>
          <h3>拥抱AI时代的创新实践</h3>
          <p>关注AIGC与智能体（Agent）技术，熟悉AI编程与Prompt设计，积极探索"AI+"应用场景。始终保持对前沿技术的好奇心，将新技术应用到实际项目中。</p>
          <div class="timeline-tags">
            <span>AIGC</span>
            <span>Agent开发</span>
            <span>AI+应用</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-light);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    right: -5%;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .about::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10%;
    left: -5%;
    width: 450px;
    height: 450px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(91, 161, 153, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--primary);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  /* 时间线布局 */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg, 
      transparent 0%,
      var(--primary) 10%,
      var(--secondary) 50%,
      var(--accent) 90%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.2);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) {
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .marker-dot {
    position: absolute;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background: white;
    border: 4px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: 3;
    box-shadow: 
      0 0 0 8px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.1),
      0 4px 15px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.25);
    animation: markerPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes markerPulse {
    0%, 100% {
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 0 8px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.1),
        0 4px 15px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.25);
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 0 15px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.05),
        0 4px 15px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.25);
    }
  }

  .marker-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .timeline-item:hover .marker-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(10deg);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.4);
  }

  .timeline-content {
    flex: 1;
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content {
    margin-left: -1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
    margin-right: -1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 40px;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border: 12px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content::before {
    left: -24px;
    border-right-color: var(--border-color);
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content::before {
    right: -24px;
    border-left-color: var(--border-color);
  }

  .timeline-content:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(46, 125, 137, 0.15);
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content:hover::before {
    border-right-color: var(--primary);
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content:hover::before {
    border-left-color: var(--primary);
  }

  .timeline-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover .timeline-badge {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-tags span {
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    background: var(--primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--primary);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-tags span:hover {
    background: var(--bg-light);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .timeline::before {
      left: 40px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      flex-direction: row !important;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
    }

    .marker-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .marker-dot {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      margin-left: 0 !important;
      margin-right: 0 !important;
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content::before,
    .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content::before {
      left: -24px;
      right: auto;
      border-right-color: var(--border-color);
      border-left-color: transparent;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
